These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
City: venice, prague, boston
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| City   | venice | prague | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different games are played: canasta, snooker, whist
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| Game   | canasta | whist | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
