.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, turtle, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Pet   | goat | turtle | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-7::.
