.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | september | january | october |

